(3, 'happy valentine\'s day', '3249798531677963027.jpg', '2023-02-14', 'C:\\wamp64\\tmp\\php3FAF.tmp', '<h2>When is Valentine&#39;s Day?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Valentine&#39;s Day is always on the same day every year -<strong>&nbsp;the 14th of February</strong>. During this time you&#39;ll find amazing deals and discounts that will help you save on fantastic gifts for your partner, family or friends!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this guide, we&#39;ll provide you with tips and inspiration on what to do on Valentine&#39;s Day with your boyfriend or girlfriend and how to write an amazing Valentine&#39;s Day card.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why is Valentine&#39;s Day celebrated?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you&nbsp;wondering,&nbsp;&quot;why do we celebrate Valentine&#39;s Day?&quot; If you&#39;re wondering who invented Valentine&#39;s Day, we&#39;ve got the answers! Saint Valentine&#39;s day was first recognised as a Christian feast by Pope Gelasius I in the year 496, and back in the 1300s Valentine&#39;s popularity grew, as courtly love spread like wildfire across the most sophisticated courts of continental Europe. It&#39;s safe to say, though, that it wasn&#39;t until the 1800s, when a retro fashion for medievalism became all the rage, that Valentine&#39;s reputation came to its own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Valentine&#39;s cards and letters became so popular in the times of Charles Dickens that he called it Cupid&#39;s Manufactory</strong>, and the production of small gifts for the occasion soon spread from Valentine&#39;s cards to flowers, chocolates, jewellery and the rest of the usual stuff. With such a rich history of letter writing, on this day of celebration,&nbsp;&lsquo;Happy Valentine&#39;s Day&rsquo; just doesn&rsquo;t cut it anymore. That&rsquo;s why we&rsquo;ve created&nbsp;<strong>a helpful list of tips on what to write in a Valentine&rsquo;s card UK.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What to get a boyfriend for Valentine&#39;s Day&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Relationships are hard, but shopping for a boyfriend or husband is harder! If you&#39;re wondering what to get a man for Valentine&#39;s day, we&#39;ve got some helpful ideas here!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-foot-locker-uk.html\"><strong>Footlocker coupons</strong></a>, you can buy Gift&nbsp;the trendiest shoes of the moment this&nbsp;valentine&#39;s day: Converse classic models and the evergreen&nbsp;Nike air force 1 - valentines day staple for 2023.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Add a coupon code to your shopping basket and you can save on things like sneakers, hoodies, caps &amp; beanies, jackets, t-shirts and sports equipment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What to write in a Valentine&#39;s Day card for your boyfriend</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>So the big day is fast approaching&nbsp;and you&rsquo;re completely stumped on what to write in a Valentine&rsquo;s card for your boyfriend, husband, dad or whoever! Have no fear, we&rsquo;ve got plenty of ideas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If they&rsquo;re romantic, something a little deeper might be called for like<strong>&nbsp;&lsquo;I wish I could give you the world for Valentine&rsquo;s Day. Will you settle for my heart?&rsquo;</strong>. Maybe&nbsp;<strong>sneak in an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-asos.html\">ASOS voucher&nbsp;</a></strong>cut out in the shape of a heart so when they open it, your &lsquo;heart&rsquo; flutters out!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For all the tech-heads out there, whose screen time has increased tenfold over lockdown, how about a cheeky<strong>&nbsp;&lsquo;To my darling, I love you nearly as much as you love your Playstation&rsquo;</strong>! Then why not use one of our&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-currys-pc-world.html\">Currys PC World discount codes</a>&nbsp;and get shopping - pick them up the latest phone, tablet, or games console!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What to write in a Valentine&rsquo;s card for your wife</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Now we&rsquo;ve got what to write in a Valentine&rsquo;s Day Card for your boyfriend sorted, let&rsquo;s move on to the perhaps more tricky part: what to write in your wife&rsquo;s Valentine&rsquo;s Day card (or girlfriend).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re in a long term relationship, why not allude to your future together with<strong>&nbsp;&lsquo;I can&rsquo;t wait to grow old with you and for all the adventures to come&rsquo;.</strong>&nbsp;Flowers and chocolates are a winning combination for a reason so join this with a&nbsp;<strong>beautiful bouquet&nbsp;</strong>without the huge price tag thanks to a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-prestige-flowers.html\">Prestige Flowers discount code</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cheesier still might be this next idea:<strong>&nbsp;&lsquo;I may not be your first date, first kiss or first love, but I just want to be your last everything.&rsquo;</strong>&nbsp;Show them you mean it by getting a flower subscription for 3 to 12 months! They don&rsquo;t even have to know the fantastic price you got it at when you saved with a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-bloom-wild.html\">Bloom &amp; Wild voucher code</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;re looking to &quot;bag&quot; yourself a few extra Brownie points with your better half this year why not check out the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-coach.html\">Coach</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bravovoucher.co.uk/discount-code-kate-spade.html\">Kate Spade offers</a>&nbsp;up for grabs?&nbsp;As well all know,&nbsp;<strong>us girls can never have too many handbags and shoes</strong>&nbsp;and your gift will get you in her good books for months!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What to get your girlfriend for Valentine&#39;s Day&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Flowers will never go out of style on Valentine&#39;s Day! Choose a&nbsp;<strong>classic bouquet of roses&nbsp;</strong>or go for something fun like a succulent arrangement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" /></p>',